":"有錢去咗外國讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d37ef4a5e69dff2db5b9d426d01fa618b8b0e6","tid":2347410,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e0f6b81c97e5f0dd6febba323be4a84fd24796d","tid":2347410,"uid":124584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T00:58:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾學店出垃圾教畜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"明專學生真係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ded6d7957fb2a10aad09ca4bb379b8d5aaa5df","tid":2347410,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba6423d12c0928e1e12d6b44fec4e61446734fe6","tid":2347410,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"「我地曾經向學校提出建議，沒想到院長同我地講若唔想帶菌反屋企，可以租酒店，仲話<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">無錢學咩人讀Nursing</span></span>嚟鬧番我地，根本就係無理取鬧」。Yellow更指當年2003年沙士所有護理實習亦馬上暫停，質疑為何醫管局會反其道而行之，認為暫緩臨床實習是唯一能保障學生及社區健康的做法。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街"}]}